Title: Fixed hostgroup columns related to hard states of services.
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: livestatus
Date: 1594637362
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0i1

Various columns of the "hostgroups" table always returned zero:

<ul>
<li>num_services_hard_ok</li>
<li>num_services_hard_warn</li>
<li>num_services_hard_crit</li>
<li>num_services_hard_unknown</li>
<li>worst_service_hard_state</li>
</ul>

This has been fixed, they return the expected values now.